from sqlglot.dialects.postgres import Postgres
from sqlglot.tokens import TokenType

# Monkey patch to add debug output
original_parse_types = Postgres.Parser._parse_types

def debug_parse_types(self, check_func=False):
    print(f"\n_parse_types called with check_func={check_func}")
    print(f"  Index before: {self._index}")
    print(f"  Current token: {self._curr.token_type if self._curr else None}")
    print(f"  Next token: {self._next.token_type if self._next else None}")
    print(f"  Prev token: {self._prev.token_type if self._prev else None}")
    
    # Call original with index saved
    index = self._index
    
    result = original_parse_types(self, check_func)
    
    print(f"  Index after: {self._index}")
    print(f"  Current token: {self._curr.token_type if self._curr else None}")
    print(f"  Result: {result}")
    return result

Postgres.Parser._parse_types = debug_parse_types

# Test with the actual SQL
pg = Postgres()
dialect = pg.parser()
sql = 'CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION test(input_a character varying DEFAULT NULL)'
tokens = pg.tokenizer.tokenize(sql)

dialect._tokens = tokens
dialect.sql = sql
dialect._index = 6
dialect._curr = tokens[6] if len(tokens) > 6 else None
dialect._prev = tokens[5] if len(tokens) > 5 else None
dialect._next = tokens[7] if len(tokens) > 7 else None

print("Tokens:")
for i, token in enumerate(tokens):
    print(f"  {i}: {token.token_type}: {token.text}")

print("\n--- Testing _parse_csv(dialect._parse_udf_kwarg) ---")
dialect._index = 6
dialect._curr = tokens[6] if len(tokens) > 6 else None
dialect._prev = tokens[5] if len(tokens) > 5 else None
dialect._next = tokens[7] if len(tokens) > 7 else None

expressions = dialect._parse_csv(dialect._parse_udf_kwarg)

print(f"\n--- Final Results ---")
print(f"Number of expressions: {len(expressions)}")
for i, expr in enumerate(expressions):
    print(f"  {i}: {type(expr).__name__}")
    if hasattr(expr, 'this'):
        print(f"     this: {expr.this}")
    if hasattr(expr, 'kind'):
        print(f"     kind: {expr.kind}")
EOF
